      "text": "（むしろ、昔より目標に近づいたから）\n（ずっとずっと強く思うようになったかも）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Rather‚ it's because I've gotten closer to my goal than before.）\n（I might have started to feel even stronger about it.）",
        "id": ""
